Introduction


Park Jin-Joo (박진주) is a South Korean actress under Prain TPC. She made her acting debut in the hit 2011 film Sunny. She is a member of the project girl group WSG Wannabe, WSG Wannabe (OASISO) and JUJU SECRET.
